                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="70r" to="85r" facs="070">Fols 70r–85r</locus><title>Seven Covenant Prayers, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሰባቱ፡ ኪዳናት:</foreign></title>
